Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE & DGi Properties are pleased to present 204 Sussex Street, Pascoe Vale, for sale via Public On-Site Auction, Thursday 14th March 2019 at 12.30PM.

This modern office/warehouse comprises of a clear span warehouse with full amenities. The property sits within the Moreland Development Precinct Plan which has made Pascoe Vale one of the most exciting suburbs to invest.

Located just off Gaffney Street, the property provides great access onto Citylink and all the major arterials. Positioned just 10km* from Melbourne's CBD, the property is perfect for those that want to occupy or invest.

Property features:
+ Total building area: 475sqm*
+ Sizable frontage of 12.5 metres* to Sussex Street
+ Open plan warehouse
+ Showroom potential
+ 3 phase power
+ Roller door entry
+ Great natural light
+ Access to major arterials
+ Highly desirable Industrial 3 Zone

Locational features:
+ Absolute premier location off Bell Street, moments from the central activity hub of Sydney Road and Coburg North Shopping Centre
+ Walking distance to Batman Train Station
+ Within close proximity to the Lincoln Mills Homemaker Centre which includes Bunnings & Officeworks

AUCTION - THURSDAY 14TH MARCH 2019 AT 12.30PM ON-SITE

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Urban Business Centre provides a unique opportunity to own your own commercial property in Pascoe Vale, the vibrant heart of Melbourne’s inner north. Perfectly situated in the centre of Pascoe Vale, Urban Business Centre is surrounded by residential development and impressive amenity, including walking distance to shopping centres, parks and multiple transport hubs.

•	Office warehouse space for lease from 202sqm*
•	Office space for lease from 50sqm*

This impressive development will feature 30 office warehouses and an iconic three storey office building with a premium ground floor café. Specifically designed to suit modern growing businesses, Urban Business Centre has been designed to meet impressive sustainability targets and will feature designer finishes on all amenities including kitchenettes.

Don’t miss your chance to be part of Pascoe Vale’s most highly sought-after business destination.

Occupy Q4 2020!

CBRE is pleased to offer 31 Essex Street, Pascoe Vale, available for lease.

- Total building area: 1,613sqm*.
- Warehouse area: 1,008sqm*.
- Modern two level office area: 240sqm*.
- Total mezzanine floor area 365sqm* can be removed to suit tenancy.
- Two (2) container height roller shutter doors.
- Three (3) phase power.
- Fifteen (15) on-site car spaces.
- Front and rear building access.
- Excellent access to City Link and surrounding major large format retailers and supermarkets.

*approx.
